Initialize all pygame inits
Initialize game settings
    - move speed
    - wall size
Initialize snake object

Start loop
    1. If snake alive, continue, else game over or you win
    (hidden step here) -> Check if paused, otherwise continue
    2. Check for event type
        2.1 Check quit game event -> quit game
        2.2 Check direction event -> change snake direction
    3. Move 1 step towards step head direction
        3.1 erase tail & draw new head
        3.2 update new picture



Helper functions
    - snake_alive
    - did_player_win

Later Implementations
    - Borders
    - Press x to start
    - Pause function